blocks.text:
November 24, 1947 - Nancy celebrates her eighth birthday with a party. Guests were:
(top row) Louise Moyer, Cindy, Chrissy Rohrer, Barbara Moyer, Margaredda Light;
(bottom row) Carolyn Wilhelm, Kathy, Lou-ise, Nancy, Carolyn Carlucci, and Susan Graul.

